The President of Afghanistan Hamid Karzai names the seven areas of Afghanistan that will pass into Afghan control from July: Kabul, Panjshir Province, Bamiyan Province, Herat, Mazar-e-Sharif, Mihtarlam and Lashkar Gah. (BBC)Colonel Gaddafi condemns the attacks as "barbaric, unjustified crusaders' aggression." (News Limited)